facts_and_links: {'Quotes': ['Brett Favre: When I met Coach Madden, we were on a bus, and he would ask questions like, "Who you got coming to the game?" I just remember I had a bunch of guys I played college ball with that came in, and I told him one of the guys that was coming in town had an uncle, a great uncle, called Uncle Rube. And, uh, somehow we got to talking about -and I don\'t want to reveal too much - but Uncle Rube had an uncharacteristically large sac. John thought that was the most hilarious thing in the world. Lo and behold, the next day, Reggie White got a sack, and he squeezed in Uncle Rube in the telecast.John Madden: [archive footage] That\'s the old Uncle Rube stuff. He just walked right into that sack.', 'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt16788570/quotes/?ref_=tt_dyk_qu'], 'Connections': ['Features CBS Evening News with Walter Cronkite (1941)', 'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt16788570/movieconnections/?ref_=tt_dyk_cnn']}
